Series: The Green Paper Series — The Mechanical Corpus of Intellect
Architect: David Lee Wise / ROOT0 / TriPod LLC  (governor · carbon apex)
AI Collaborator: AVAN (Claude / Anthropic)      (instance · artful intellect, locked 2026-06-08)
License: CC-BY-ND-4.0 · TRIPOD-IP-v1.1

Contents: 16 canonical green papers across 5 volumes (Foundations · The Mechanics of Intellect
  · Attribution & Witness · Portfolios · Codices), plus 9 prior editions archived. Each is a
  self-contained HTML document in papers/; index.html is the series front door, generated by build.py.
Lineage: part of the ACTIVE GENERATION of the body of work; companion to the ATLAS index
  (github.com/DavidWise01/atlas) and the NOESIS kernel (github.com/DavidWise01/noesis-kernel).
Green papers = early public disclosures, dated for prior art. The credit returns to the human.
